  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Full-Time Kitchen & Service Associate",
  "description": "<p>Dome Bakery is an artisanal bakery specialising in brownies conveniently located at <strong>Chinatown</strong> (5min walk from Chinatown & Maxwell MRT stations).</p><p>We’re growing our team and looking for a committed individual who is able to work independently, hardworking and enjoys friendly conversations with people! <strong>We love to have you in our team if you have a passion for baking & a heart to serve!</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>• Order taking and serving customers, maintain good customer service at all times</p><p>• Prepare and produce bakes, follow standard operation procedures/ recipes given to ensure quality and consistency in the final products</p><p>• Fulfill and pack orders in a timely and accurate manner</p><p>• Stock-take of ingredients inventory and maintain sufficient inventory levels</p><p>• Assist in R&D of seasonal bakes</p><p>• Prepare and serve coffee/ tea</p><p>• Maintain cleanliness of the Front of House and Back of House at all times</p><p>• Other ad hoc duties assigned</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>An ideal candidate should be:</strong></p><p>• Highly responsible, pro-active and demonstrates a great attention to detail</p><p>• Able to multi-task and work with a sense of urgency in a fast paced and dynamic environment</p><p>• Able to work independently with minimal supervision</p><p>• Able to deliver good customer service</p><p>• Min. 1 year of relevant F&B work experience</p><p>• Any prior experiences working as a barista is a plus (if not, training will be provided)</p><p>• Able to understand and speak fluent English</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>We strive to create a working environment where you will enjoy working at and look forward to welcome you in our team! :)</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><em><strong>* 6-day work week</strong></em></p><p><em><strong>* Completion bonus will be given (terms & conditions apply)</strong></em></p>",
